<br>
---Let me give you a tiny bit of history before I begin to rant. We have a user (we're an ISP and computer repair shop, among other things) who likes to come in from time to time and ask us if we have any used Pentium IIIs and used 19&quot; monitors for chump change. He never actually buys anything, but he likes to ask.<br>
<br>
---Last month he called on the phone and actually wanted me to explain to him how to make a web database and make it work... over the phone, real quick. He knows NOTHING AT ALL about this stuff. He probably heard the word &quot;database&quot; from television. Anyway, he wanted me to make a web-based business for him and let him make all the money, regardless of the fact he had no idea what he was asking, talking about or insinuating. He didn't even know what he would put in this &quot;database&quot;. He's a get-rich-quick kind of guy who MIGHT have graduated highschool. He wanted all this on the phone, for no money, as if this was normal tech support question material.<br>
<br>
---Today he calls me up and asks how to connect two computers together via a phone line. I ask a little further and he delves into this...<br>
<br>
&quot;I want to make an ISP, but I don't think I know how.&quot;<br>
<br>
---Honest to the Lord Almighty, he thought he could run an ISP off his 486 with his regular old phone line at HOME.<br>
<br>
Crack kills ! <p><IMG SRC="http://www.premiernet.net/~chandler/images/newmaclogo3.gif"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ubalgair.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Balgair</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Warlord</span><br>  Posts: 140<br> <font color=#330000>(7/27/01 7:10:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/ftheclanmacleargeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1123.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://eo.yifan.net/users/q/balgair/Bal60x60.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: So dumb, it actually baffles me.</span><hr size=1> At least he admits his ignorance :-) :-)<br>
